item.title: Windsurfing brave Devon for the Aussie Kiss
item.author: Dolo Garcia,
item.description: On the 20th of October, the Imperial windsurfing Team adventured to the confined lands of Devon to participate in the biggest Student Windsurfing Festival of the year: the Student Windsurfing Association’s Aussie Kiss! Everything looked perfect – 360 windsurfers from all over the UK were about and …
